description:
Viewer for Microsoft® Project

MOOS Project Viewer is a viewer for Microsoft® Project that allows you to open, view in a dynamic way and print any Microsoft® Project file. It is running on any Java enabled platform including Windows®, Mac OS X and Linux. There are many viewers for Microsoft® Project on the market, some freeware and others commercial. MOOS Project Viewer is the best choice in terms of features per price. But don't just take our word for it. Try it yourself!
